					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The color video signal is generated by 12 different possible square waves, each is delayed 0 to 11 master clock cycles.  They can be at 4 different brightness levels.  So that's 48 colors there.<br />Then the first column has no color and is only gray, it has three different brightness levels, then a second copy of white.<br />Then there's that column that has weird black (blacker than black), black, and two gray levels.<br />Then the rest of the colors are all black for some reason.</div>

					
